title: Female Racing Duo Team Larsen Has the Need for Speed
text:
Female Racing Duo Team Larsen Has the Need for Speed 
By John Evenson/CBS12Jupiter, Fla. (CBS12) - The need for speed is being taken to a whole new level at Palm Beach International Raceway, and you might be shocked at who the home town favorites are. The Female duo of Team Larsen are using Jet engines to break records for speed, and create all types of fire on the track."Why would you want to strap yourself to like land lot missle that goes almost 300 miles per hour down the drag strip? It's addrenaline baby," says Elaine Larsen, who's been racing jet dragsters for 13 years now, "it feeds through my veins, this is what I was born to do."Jet dragsters go from 0 to 290 miles per hour in 5.5 seconds, and the feeling is unbelievable according to Larsen."It's 7 negative G's when you pull that parachute. Honey your heart doesn't start thumping until a few minutes after."And while all this firey speed is very impressive, the most unlikely of mad scientists is behind it all. 22 year old Paige Sanchez is a self professed speed nerd."I've always been an engineering nerd," admits Sanchez, "I love love math and science, to drive it would be something that I wouldn't want to do as much I love the mechanics behind it , I love the engineering I love the aeropack, that's what I really love."An she also like to keep Eliane as safe as possible.The 2-time World champ is still reaching impossible speeds after a serious accident almost ended her life."I hit a wall at 280 miles per hour and I actually had brain surgery," says Larsen, "I have a tytanium plate in my head.""Everytime I pack these parachute, everytime I work on this car I have Elaine Larsens life in my hand," says Sanchez, "and do you know how intimidating that is having the bosses life in your hands.""There is no gimmick about Paige and I," adds Larsen, "we are the real deal we drive the rig to our races, we set the rid up, we do everything on this race car. If you can't put up, than you get up and you go somewhere else."Either way, Team Larsen will be leaving you in the dust. Female Racing Duo Team Larsen Has the Need for Speed
